"},{"pid":"0581aa9a6c1b2b60ae29a47fa25b2d8d46982dc9","tid":454633,"uid":2059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T23:49:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/164051_67324f8d045c3956f25e3ef9b176bac8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F164051_67324f8d045c3956f25e3ef9b176bac8.jpg&h=e17f32b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我家砵子，係屯門康和做，淨手術要480，手術前會抽血睇砵子有無d咩病，抽血好像680<br />\n<br />\n做完之後第二日精神番哂黎，食得訓得屙得！</blockquote><br />\n我隻貓仔貓女都係康和做<br />\n<br />\n貓女絕育個陣有d發情跡象，睇唔出，<br />\n但醫生話個子宮發大+腫左（好似係），手術會難d<br />\n所以收貴左幾舊水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過肚仔傷口都算做得唔錯，好快好返"}]}